<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF108-059-612  </DOCNO><DOCID>08 059 612.andM;</DOCID><JOURNAL>Digital Review  Jan 8 1990 v7 n1 p29(1)* Full Text COPYRIGHT Cahners-Ziff Publishing Associates LP 1990.andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>ESS' data recovery, conversion services aid DEC compatibles.andO;(Electronic Service Specialists Ltd.)andO;</TITLE><AUTHOR>Mansfield, Clare.andM;</AUTHOR><DESCRIPT>Company:   Electronic Service Specialists Ltd. (services).andO;Topic:     Data RecoverySupport ServicesService Industry.andM;</DESCRIPT><TEXT>ESS' Data Recovery, Conversion Services Aid DEC CompatiblesandM;MENOMONEE FALLS, Wis.andP;  -- For those users bemoaning the loss of invaluabledata--whether from fire, flooding or just everyday carelessness--ElectronicService Specialists (ESS) has added a data recovery service to itsrepertoire.andM;Most data loss victims have to contend with damaged disk heads, said WarrenHaeberle, ESS' president.andP;  The problems can result from a system malfunction,an operator's negligence or a natural disaster.andM;The customer's first response is to turn to the backup disk, Haeberle said.andO;But sometimes backup disk data is entered improperly or incompletely, hesaid.andM;ESS technicians extract data from damaged heads and transfer it to anotherdisk or tape.andP;  ESS offers this service for all DEC systems and DEC-compatibleperipherals.andM;The technicians test disks to see if they can still fly and to ascertain whatdata is retrievable and what is lost permanently, said Jeffrey Bieringer,ESS' director of technical services.andM;ESS determines service charges according to time and materials used,Bieringer said.andP;  For example, transferring and recovering data from a 150MBdrive to magnetic tape is not very labor-intensive, he said, and ESS wouldcharge approximately $1,000.andM;Recovering 50 percent to 80 percent of a 500MB drive is much morelabor-intensive, however, Bieringer said, and ESS would therefore chargeabout $5,000.andM;The company has also announced a media conversion service that will helpbusinesses convert files from one media to a new format.andP;  Prices for theservice are based on time and materials.andM;Electronic Service Specialists Ltd. is located at N92 W14612 Anthony Ave.,andO;Menomonee Falls, WI 53051, (414) 255-4634.andO;</TEXT></DOC>